# 止蝕  
(pos:動詞)  
<explanation>  
yue: 唔再虧本，喺投資或買賣入面，當虧蝕到某一程度時，主動賣出資產，避免虧蝕繼續擴大（量詞：次）  
eng: to cut losses (in investing or trading) by selling an asset to prevent further losses  

<eg>  
yue: 股價跌到$10，佢就即刻止蝕，唔使再虧多啲。 (zi2 sik1 jau5 $10, keoi5 zau6 haak1 zi2 sik1, m4 saai1 wui4 wai1 dou1 di2.)  
eng: When the stock price dropped to $10, he immediately cut his losses so he wouldn’t lose any more.  

yue: 唔好執著，見到虧到兩成就止蝕，留住本金先至緊要。 (m4 hou2 zip3 zek3, gin3 dou3 fai1 dou3 jing5 si1 zi2 sik1, lau4 zyu6 bun2 ceon1 sin1 zi2 jing2 jiu3.)  
eng: Don’t be stubborn — if you’ve lost 20%, cut your losses straight away; preserving your capital’s the most important thing. [end of text]


